					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Zepper is one of them, having made a successful Windows emulator, and the original documentation was his.<br /><br />You are correct that I made a mistake in that I didn't count the 7 cycles to enter an IRQ. However you also made a mistake, there are 19 nops, not 20.<br /><br />PHA = 3<br />19 NOPS = 19 * 2<br />4 LDA #imm = 2 * 4<br />4 STA ABS = 4 * 4<br /><br />3 + 19*2 + 2*4 + 4*4 = 65<br />65 * 3 = 195</div>

